title: Ep. - 511 - JEN SHAH PLEA WITH EMILY D. BAKER EXECUTIVE PRODUCER OF AMERICAN NINJA WARRIOR
description:
Attorney Emily D. Baker discusses the latest update in Real Housewives of Salt Lake City star Jen Shah’s case. Shah plead guilty to criminal fraud charges stemming from an alleged telemarketing scheme.

 

Executive Producer Brian Richardson discusses season 14 of American Ninja Warrior where some of the most elite athletes in the country compete on the world’s most difficult obstacle courses.
